<span class="displaytext">the (candidate last) campaign today announced the endorsement of california congressman brad sherman. <p>"senator (candidate full) has the strength and experience to lead america in a new direction and create the change this country needs," rep. sherman said. "her 35-year record of advocacy makes her uniquely equipped to hit the ground running on her first day in the white house." </p><p>now in his sixth term, rep. sherman serves as chairman of the house subcommittee on terrorism, nonproliferation and trade, and is a senior member of the house financial services committee. one of the few certified public accountants in congress, rep. sherman has pushed for fiscal responsibility and a fairer tax code. </p><p>"congressman sherman has been a leader in congress in his efforts to protect our environment, and a respected voice on foreign and fiscal policy," (candidate last) said. "i am honored to have his support and delighted he'll help lead our efforts in california."</p></span>



